    "description": "庆祝动画「NARUTO火影忍者」20周年的「终极风暴」系列终极版登场！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■新增数个可游玩的角色，全系列最多的忍者在此集合</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1020790/extras/dbf532046abe99c0859db51ee877822a.poster.avif?t=1727301927\" width=616 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1020790/extras/dbf532046abe99c0859db51ee877822a.webm?t=1727301927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1020790/extras/dbf532046abe99c0859db51ee877822a.mp4?t=1727301927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>本作有超过130个忍者可操控，以及惊心动魄的忍道对战！除了内容丰富的网络对战，还增加操作模式「简单」，可用简单的操作发动各种忍术连击。无论是系列老玩家或初次接触的玩家，都能用自己喜爱的角色享受热血对战。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■以超越动画水平重新编辑鸣人与佐助的故事</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1020790/extras/87788aebfd2fb19c888ad3e24d0e63b3.poster.avif?t=1727301927\" width=616 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1020790/extras/87788aebfd2fb19c888ad3e24d0e63b3.webm?t=1727301927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1020790/extras/87788aebfd2fb19c888ad3e24d0e63b3.mp4?t=1727301927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>「终极风暴」系列中，以动画截图与「终极风暴开发团队全力打造的原作体验战斗」，描绘整个「火影忍者」故事。本作节选了从少年篇到最终决战的所有精彩场面。将可体验原作中两人的忍道。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■收录新世代的特殊故事</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1020790/extras/528811f6f5b1bd8a5d1eb3db9f7d4c30.poster.avif?t=1727301927\" width=616 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1020790/extras/528811f6f5b1bd8a5d1eb3db9f7d4c30.webm?t=1727301927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1020790/extras/528811f6f5b1bd8a5d1eb3db9f7d4c30.mp4?t=1727301927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>第七代火影的儿子──漩涡慕留人在火红的网络游戏「忍者英雄」中与一名少女相遇，最后却卷入影响全忍界的大战……请体验再次集合的终极风暴开发团队的作品，超越动画演出的原创剧情。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■另一个火影忍者粉丝们的最爱就是自订系统！</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1020790/extras/5beb447cf49938ffa068314629367f0b.poster.avif?t=1727301927\" width=616 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1020790/extras/5beb447cf49938ffa068314629367f0b.webm?t=1727301927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>玩家在冒险途中，可获得外观自订道具的对战奖励。<br>这些道具可打造出「NARUTO X BORUTO 火影忍者 终极风暴羁绊」独一无二的特殊体验。",
